Package emotionalsongs.components.appnav

Class AppNav

java.lang.Object
com.vaadin.flow.component.Component
emotionalsongs.components.appnav.AppNav
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.vaadin.flow.component.AttachNotifier, com.vaadin.flow.component.DetachNotifier, com.vaadin.flow.component.HasElement, com.vaadin.flow.component.HasSize, com.vaadin.flow.component.HasStyle, Serializable
@JsModule("@vaadin-component-factory/vcf-nav") @Tag("vcf-nav") @NpmPackage(value="@vaadin-component-factory/vcf-nav", version="1.0.6") public class AppNav extends com.vaadin.flow.component.Component implements com.vaadin.flow.component.HasSize, com.vaadin.flow.component.HasStyle
Version:
1.0
Author:
Acquati Luca, Jamil Muhammad Qasim, Naturale Lorenzo, Volonterio Luca

Questa classe rappresenta il componente di navigazione AppNav. È un componente Vaadin che offre funzionalità di navigazione avanzate. Utilizza il modulo JavaScript "@vaadin-component-factory/vcf-nav".

See Also:
